actions.name: qradar.retrieveRules
actions.display_name: Retrieves a list of rules

actions.name: qradar.CreateCasesFromOffenses
actions.display_name: Get offenses from QRadar and create Cases

actions.name: qradar.QradarOffensesList
actions.display_name: Gets offenses from QRadar.

actions.name: qradar.QradarOffenseUpdate
actions.display_name: Updates an offense.

actions.name: qradar.QradarClosingReasons
actions.display_name: Retrieves a list of offense closing reasons.

actions.name: qradar.QradarOffenseNotesList
actions.display_name: Retrieves a list of notes for an offense.

actions.name: qradar.QradarOffenseNoteCreate
actions.display_name: Creates a note on an offense.

actions.name: qradar.QradarRuleGroupsList
actions.display_name: Retrieves a list of the rule groups.

actions.name: qradar.QradarAssetsList
actions.display_name: Retrieves assets list.

actions.name: qradar.QradarSavedSearchesList
actions.display_name: Retrieves a list of Ariel saved searches.

actions.name: qradar.QradarSearchesList
actions.display_name: Retrieves the list of Ariel searches IDs. Search status and results can be polled by sending the search ID to the 'qradar-search-status-get' and 'qradar-search-results-get' commands.

actions.name: qradar.QradarSearchCreate
actions.display_name: Creates a new asynchronous Ariel search. Returns the search ID. Search status and results can be polled by sending the search ID to the 'qradar-search-status-get' and 'qradar-search-results-get' commands. Accepts SELECT query expressions only.

actions.name: qradar.QradarSearchStatusGet
actions.display_name: Retrieves status information for a search, based on the search ID.

actions.name: qradar.QradarSearchResultsGet
actions.display_name: Retrieves search results.

actions.name: qradar.QradarReferenceSetsList
actions.display_name: Retrieves a list of reference sets.

actions.name: qradar.QradarReferenceSetCreate
actions.display_name: Creates a new reference set.

actions.name: qradar.QradarReferenceSetDelete
actions.display_name: Removes a reference set or purges its contents.

actions.name: qradar.QradarReferenceSetValueUpsert
actions.display_name: Adds or updates an element in a reference set.

actions.name: qradar.QradarReferenceSetValueDelete
actions.display_name: Removes a value from a reference set.

actions.name: qradar.QradarIndicatorsUpload
actions.display_name: Uploads indicators to QRadar.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGeolocationsForIp
actions.display_name: Retrieves the MaxMind GeoIP data for the specified IP address.

actions.name: qradar.QradarLogSourcesList
actions.display_name: Retrieves a list of log sources.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetCustomProperties
actions.display_name: Retrieves a list of event regex properties.

actions.name: qradar.QradarResetLastRun
actions.display_name: Resets the fetch incidents last run value, which resets the fetch to its initial fetch state. (Will try to fetch the first available offense).

actions.name: qradar.GetMappingFields
actions.display_name: Returns the list of fields for an incident type. This command should be used for debugging purposes.

actions.name: qradar.QradarOffenses
actions.display_name: Gets offenses from QRadar.

actions.name: qradar.QradarOffenseById
actions.display_name: Gets offense with matching offense ID from qradar.

actions.name: qradar.QradarUpdateOffense
actions.display_name: Update an offense.

actions.name: qradar.QradarSearches
actions.display_name: Searches in QRadar using AQL. It is highly recommended to use the playbook 'QRadarFullSearch' instead of this command - it will execute the search, and will return the result.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetSearch
actions.display_name: Gets a specific search id and status.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetSearchResults
actions.display_name: Gets search results.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetAssets
actions.display_name: List all assets found in the model.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetAssetById
actions.display_name: Retrieves the asset by id.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetClosingReasons
actions.display_name: Get closing reasons.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetNote
actions.display_name: Retrieve a note for an offense.

actions.name: qradar.QradarCreateNote
actions.display_name: Create a note on an offense.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetReferenceByName
actions.display_name: Information about the reference set that had data added or updated. This returns the information set, but not the contained data. This feature is supported from version 8.1 and upward.

actions.name: qradar.QradarCreateReferenceSet
actions.display_name: Creates a new reference set. If the provided name is already in use, this command will fail.

actions.name: qradar.QradarDeleteReferenceSet
actions.display_name: Deletes a reference set corresponding to the name provided.

actions.name: qradar.QradarCreateReferenceSetValue
actions.display_name: Add or update a value in a reference set.

actions.name: qradar.QradarUpdateReferenceSetValue
actions.display_name: Adds or updates a value in a reference set.

actions.name: qradar.QradarDeleteReferenceSetValue
actions.display_name: Deletes a value in a reference set.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetDomains
actions.display_name: Retrieve all Domains.

actions.name: qradar.QradarGetDomainById
actions.display_name: Retrieves Domain information By ID.

actions.name: qradar.QradarUploadIndicators
actions.display_name: Uploads indicators from Demisto to Qradar.

actions.name: qradar.QradarDomainsList
actions.display_name: Retrieve all Domains.

actions.name: qradar.GetRemoteData
actions.display_name: Gets remote data from a remote incident. This method does not update the current incident, and should be used for debugging purposes.

actions.name: qradar.GetModifiedRemoteData
actions.display_name: Returns the list of incidents IDs that were modified since the last update time. Note that this method is for debugging purposes. The get-modified-remote-data command is used as part of the mirroring feature, which is available from version 6.1.

actions.name: qraadar.QradarRulesList
actions.display_name: Retrieves a list of rules.
